<lb n="0255c07"/><head type="no">No. 1254</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0255c08"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0255024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第十六，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，（佛說）＋末【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0255024"><lem>末</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">佛說末</rdg></app><note n="0255024" place="foot" type="rest">麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第十六，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>利支提婆華鬘經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0255c09"/>
<lb n="0255c10"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0255025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…寺））三十七字＝（（唐））一字【明】【乙】，〔開府…智〕三十三字－【甲】</note><note n="0255025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺）三十七字＝（（唐））一字【明】【乙】，〔開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智〕三十三字－【甲】</note><app n="0255025"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0255c11"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0255c12"/>正號大廣智大興善<note n="0255026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔寺〕－【甲】</note><app n="0255026"><lem>寺</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唐</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺</rdg></app>三藏沙<note n="0255027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＋（大廣智）【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0255027"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0255c13"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0255c14"/><p>如是我聞。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。
<lb n="0255c15"/>與大阿羅漢二百五十人俱。復有無量大菩薩
<lb n="0255c16"/>眾。彌勒菩薩曼殊室利菩薩觀世音菩薩而為
<lb n="0255c17"/>上首。及末利支等諸天龍神八部前後圍遶。</p>
<lb n="0255c18"/><p>爾時舍利子即從座起遍袒右肩。右膝著地
<lb n="0255c19"/>合掌而白佛言。世尊。未來末世眾生作何法
<lb n="0255c20"/>得脫諸難。佛告舍利子諦聽諦聽。我今為汝
<lb n="0255c21"/>說於此事。爾時眾會歡喜踊躍重復勸請。時
<lb n="0255c22"/>佛世尊即說此言。有天名末利支。常在日前
<lb n="0255c23"/>行。日不見彼彼能見日即說&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0255c24"/><lg><l>南謨佛陀耶</l><l>南謨達<note n="0255028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝磨【明】【乙】</note><app n="0255028"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">磨</rdg></app>耶</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0256a" n="0256a"/>
<lb n="0256a01"/><l>南謨僧伽耶</l></lg>
<lb n="0256a02"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他阿囉迦摩斯末迦摩斯阿豆摩
<lb n="0256a03"/>斯支婆羅摩斯安達檀那摩斯摩利支波羅摩
<lb n="0256a04"/>斯那<note n="0256001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漠＝謨【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256001"><lem>漠</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">謨</rdg></app>率都羝娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0256002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）細註【明】【乙】＊</note><note n="0256002" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>賀＋（引）細註【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0256002"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0256a05"/><p>王難中覆護我。賊難行路難失路曠野。晝日
<lb n="0256a06"/>夜中水難火難。羅剎難<note n="0256003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（鳩盤）＋茶【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256003"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">鳩盤茶</rdg></app><note n="0256004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雞＝難【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256004"><lem>雞</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">難</rdg></app>支&CB00135;鬼難中
<lb n="0256a07"/>毒藥難。佛語真實法語真實僧<note n="0256005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">實語＝語真實【明】【乙】，語實【甲】</note><note n="0256005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">實語＝語真實【明】【乙】，＝語實【甲】</note><app n="0256005"><lem>實語</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">語真實</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">語實</rdg></app>。天實語
<lb n="0256a08"/>仙人實語覆護我&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0256a09"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;<note n="0256006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256006"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<note n="0256007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔反〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256007"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>他阿羅拘利阿羅拘利吉利的
<lb n="0256a10"/>羝勒叉勒叉我某甲薩婆婆油<note n="0256008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256008"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00425;陀羅菩
<lb n="0256a11"/>提婆伽夜栖<note n="0256009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔斯亞反〕－【明】</note><app n="0256009"><lem><note place="inline">斯亞反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>裨<note n="0256010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔毘〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256010"><lem><note place="inline">毘</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>馺婆賀</p>
<lb n="0256a12"/><p>佛言若有人欲行此法者。一切法中此法最
<lb n="0256a13"/>勝。若人欲得供養末利支天者。應用金若銀
<lb n="0256a14"/>若赤銅若白檀若紫檀。應<note n="0256011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＝用【明】</note><app n="0256011"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">用</rdg></app>末利支天形像。
<lb n="0256a15"/>其造像法。一似天女形。身長大小一寸二寸
<lb n="0256a16"/>三寸乃至一肘。其中最勝者一寸二寸為好。
<lb n="0256a17"/>其作像又須得最好手博士。遣受八戒齋日
<lb n="0256a18"/>日洗浴。著淨白衣作之。其價直之者隨博士
<lb n="0256a19"/>語索不得<note n="0256012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">違＋（價）【明】【乙】，違＝還價【甲】</note><app n="0256012"><lem>違</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">違價</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">還價</rdg></app>。作此像已。若苾芻欲行遠<note n="0256013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔道〕－【甲】</note><app n="0256013"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0256a20"/>於袈裟片中裹著彼像。若<note n="0256014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔持〕－【甲】</note><app n="0256014"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>五戒優婆塞。於
<lb n="0256a21"/>頭髻中盛著彼像。大小便時離身放著。不得
<lb n="0256a22"/>共身上<note n="0256015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">屏＝廁【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256015"><lem>屏</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">廁</rdg></app>大小便利。</p>
<lb n="0256a23"/><p>次說印及壇法。</p>
<lb n="0256a24"/><p><note n="0256016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">交＝反【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0256016"><lem>交</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app>叉二小指二無名指。在掌中右押左。二頭
<lb n="0256a25"/>指直&CB00594;頭相著。二中指各&CB03366;在二頭指背上
<lb n="0256a26"/>頭相拄著。二大指並&CB00594;<note n="0256017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝搏【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0256017"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">搏</rdg></app>二頭指側。大指來
<lb n="0256a27"/>去。此是身姥陀羅<note n="0256018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尼印＝用【甲】</note><app n="0256018"><lem>尼<note n="0256019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256019"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">用</rdg></app>准前身印。<note n="0256020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0256020" corr="＆lac；" resp="【乙】">上</sic>各屈
<lb n="0256a28"/>二中指上節。頭向大指垂甲<note n="0256021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＝指【明】</note><app n="0256021"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">指</rdg></app>背。<note n="0256022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又＝叉【明】</note><app n="0256022"><lem>又</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">叉</rdg></app>屈二
<lb n="0256a29"/>大指上節。頭向掌中。此是<note n="0256023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔頭〕－【甲】</note><app n="0256023"><lem>頭</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>頂印。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0256b" n="0256b"/>
<lb n="0256b01"/><p>若比丘比丘尼。袈裟中裹前像。若俗人頭髻
<lb n="0256b02"/>中著像。即作此頭印以案像上。二十一遍誦
<lb n="0256b03"/>&CB00057;行於道路。准前身印唯開二頭指頭二分
<lb n="0256b04"/>許。即是護身印用之護身法。</p>
<lb n="0256b05"/><p>左手大指頭押無名指第一節文。以餘四指把
<lb n="0256b06"/>拳即是歡喜印。若作此印誦&CB00057;向王臣邊者。
<lb n="0256b07"/>即前人歡喜左手屈臂牽向於前。以頭指已
<lb n="0256b08"/>下四指把拳。復以大指押頭指甲上。次開掌
<lb n="0256b09"/>中作孔。以右手申掌。從左手<note n="0256024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（指）＋節&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0256024" corr="指節" resp="【乙】">節</sic>上向。手掌
<lb n="0256b10"/><note n="0256025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝摩【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0256025"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>之到於孔上。即以右掌覆蓋指孔上。心
<lb n="0256b11"/>作之。左手掌是末利支心。右手掌是末利支
<lb n="0256b12"/>身。於左手掌心中。我身隨<note n="0256026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔在〕－&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0256026"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>末利支天藏我
<lb n="0256b13"/>身著。末利支在我頂上護於我身。此是末利
<lb n="0256b14"/>支印。口中數數誦&CB00057;者即得大驗。行者不得
<lb n="0256b15"/>喫飯。唯食大麥乳酪酥菜<note n="0256027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等＝得&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0256027"><lem>等</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">得</rdg></app>。若不堪忍者自
<lb n="0256b16"/>乞飯喫。不得喫於眾僧之食。如是滿足十萬
<lb n="0256b17"/>遍即得驗也。於淨潔道場中安末利支像。已
<lb n="0256b18"/>行者日日洗浴。<note n="0256028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若不洗浴〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256028"><lem>若不洗浴</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>洗手漱口入道場。
<lb n="0256b19"/>作身印喚末利支。安置已種種供養。日日誦
<lb n="0256b20"/>&CB00057;一百八遍或一千<note n="0256029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＋（十）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256029"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">八十</rdg></app>遍。如是乃至滿十萬
<lb n="0256b21"/>遍訖。然後於好處所料理於地。拔去惡物樹
<lb n="0256b22"/>根瓦礫毛骨等已。堅築於地使平坦之。其作
<lb n="0256b23"/>壇日者臘月十五日。以五色作之。中心著末
<lb n="0256b24"/>利支座。座上畫著華座并像。<note n="0256030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">式＝或【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256030"><lem>式</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">或</rdg></app>即東面安使
<lb n="0256b25"/>者。名婆多羅室利夜。北面安使者。名計室&CB00135;。
<lb n="0256b26"/>南面安使者。名摩利&CB00135;。然後&CB00057;師喚之安置。
<lb n="0256b27"/>以香華飲食八槃燈十六盞。種種供養已。&CB00057;
<lb n="0256b28"/>師在西門面向東坐。誦&CB00057;一千八遍。種種供
<lb n="0256b29"/>養訖然後發遣之。更有別法日月蝕日。作此
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0256c" n="0256c"/>
<lb n="0256c01"/>壇法者大得驗也。</p>
<lb n="0256c02"/><p>若人欲東西遠行<note n="0256031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔在〕－【甲】</note><app n="0256031"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>路者。先作水壇。喚末利
<lb n="0256c03"/>支安置已。取粳米華和酥。&CB00057;一遍一燒滿一
<lb n="0256c04"/>千八遍并誦&CB00057;。隨所欲去處趣者得大驗。</p>
<lb n="0256c05"/><p>又更一法七日之中日日作水壇。喚末利支
<lb n="0256c06"/>安置。復著火爐然穀木樹火。於此柴火中。&CB00057;
<lb n="0256c07"/>燒粳米烏麻一百八遍并誦&CB00057;。日三時時別
<lb n="0256c08"/>一百八遍。乃至七日作此法訖。向王臣邊者
<lb n="0256c09"/>前人散走<note n="0256032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＝也【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0256032"><lem>他</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0256c10"/><p>又更一法若欲論議。依前法火燒梨枝一百
<lb n="0256c11"/>八段。<note n="0256033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一段〕－【甲】</note><app n="0256033"><lem>一段</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一<note n="0256034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尺＝擲【明】【乙】</note><app n="0256034"><lem>尺</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">擲</rdg></app>并&CB00057;七日。作此法者得大
<lb n="0256c12"/>論師也。</p>
<lb n="0256c13"/><p>又法依前法火燒酥一百八遍并&CB00057;者。一切
<lb n="0256c14"/>禽獸毒蟲不得侵害。</p>
<lb n="0256c15"/><p>又法若人欲得見末利支者。依前法以穀樹
<lb n="0256c16"/>柴然火。取天木二十一段。以酥蜜酪塗之。火
<lb n="0256c17"/>燒并&CB00057;日日。唯喫粳米飯乳<note n="0256035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＝酪【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0256035"><lem>酥</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">酪</rdg></app>三種。不得食
<lb n="0256c18"/>餘物。七日之中日日倍勝種種供養。如是七
<lb n="0256c19"/>日作此法時。第七日中末利支身現。入道場
<lb n="0256c20"/>問行者言。汝欲求何法。是時行者隨意答之。
<lb n="0256c21"/>時末利支聽許歸去即知得驗。一切諸天亦
<lb n="0256c22"/>皆歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0256c23"/><p>又法七日之中每日三時。火燒茴香草白菖
<lb n="0256c24"/>蒲白芥子三種。并&CB00057;訖向羅闍邊去者前人
<lb n="0256c25"/>歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0256c26"/><p>又法欲向官人邊去者。依前法火燒白芥子。
<lb n="0256c27"/>日日三時時別一百八遍并&CB00057;。七日之中唯
<lb n="0256c28"/>食粳米乳酪三種。不得食餘物。如是七日訖
<lb n="0256c29"/>向官人邊去者前人歡喜。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0257a" n="0257a"/>
<lb n="0257a01"/><p>又法依前法。火燒阿末羅梨葉一百八遍并
<lb n="0257a02"/>&CB00057;。<note n="0257001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（&CB00057;）＋如【明】【乙】</note><app n="0257001"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;如</rdg></app>是七日治一切鬼病則得驗。</p>
<lb n="0257a03"/><p>又法依前法。取大麥好擣<note n="0257002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勿使末三字明本作本文</note><note n="0257002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（勿使末）三字夾註＝（勿使末）三字本文【明】</note><app n="0257002"><lem><note place="inline">勿使末</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">勿使末</rdg></app>以蜜和作團。
<lb n="0257a04"/>大如李子一百八箇。七日之中行者初日全
<lb n="0257a05"/>不喫食。餘六日任意得食。日日火燒所團大
<lb n="0257a06"/>麥并&CB00057;。作上歡喜印如是盡燒一百八團訖。
<lb n="0257a07"/>以水滅火後附其煙上薰兩手掌。誦&CB00057;二十
<lb n="0257a08"/>一遍。願云使<note n="0257003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＝者【甲】</note><app n="0257003"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>之手作一切法種種得驗者。
<lb n="0257a09"/>即一切得驗前人歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0257a10"/><p>又法若人熱病。取好青草擬口。誦&CB00057;二十一
<lb n="0257a11"/>遍。以摩病者五十四遍并&CB00057;者即差。</p>
<lb n="0257a12"/><p>又法日日一遍誦&CB00057;。<note n="0257004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0257004" corr="二" resp="【乙】">三</sic>遍作大護身。三遍作
<lb n="0257a13"/>大結界。五遍誦&CB00057;者所愛之人任意即得。六
<lb n="0257a14"/>遍誦&CB00057;結界。夜入塚墓一切無畏。</p>
<lb n="0257a15"/><p>又法若欲遠行。先於私房七遍火燒薰陸之
<lb n="0257a16"/>香并&CB00057;訖。著道行之時數數誦&CB00057;行者。路中
<lb n="0257a17"/>賊難鬼難等皆不得近也。</p>
<lb n="0257a18"/><p>又法依前法。白月八日於淨室中。取好香花
<lb n="0257a19"/>與粳米飯少少。火燒一千八遍。行法之人一
<lb n="0257a20"/>日不食。著淨潔之衣作此法者。前人尊重恭
<lb n="0257a21"/>敬供養。</p>
<lb n="0257a22"/><p>又法取牛糞未落地時。以器承取莫著別處。
<lb n="0257a23"/>即用和水作水壇。壇中心著佛像或佛舍利。
<lb n="0257a24"/>復取母犢<note n="0257005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">並＝并【明】【乙】</note><app n="0257005"><lem>並</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">并</rdg></app>黃牛乳作酥。盛著金&CB00425;中。以右
<lb n="0257a25"/>手無名指攪之。於酥并&CB00057;。其酥之上火若出
<lb n="0257a26"/>者。即知得大聰明<note n="0257006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝曰&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0257006" corr="曰" resp="【乙】">一</sic>誦千偈。若火不出唯煙
<lb n="0257a27"/>與煖者。即<note n="0257007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔知〕－【甲】</note><app n="0257007"><lem>知</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得<note n="0257008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">可＋（可）【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0257008"><lem>可</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">可可</rdg></app>聰明。若不得煙煖。自身
<lb n="0257a28"/>伏地擬口於酥器邊。以右手無名指為<note n="0257009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01746;＝著【明】，箸【乙】</note><note n="0257009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01746;＝著【明】，＝箸【乙】</note><app n="0257009"><lem>&CB01746;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">箸</rdg></app>喫
<lb n="0257a29"/>酥。即得少少聰明。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0257b" n="0257b"/>
<lb n="0257b01"/><p>又法於城東門外。好料理地作四肘壇。取坏
<lb n="0257b02"/>塼五箇。中心著一四面各一。又以四水罐盛
<lb n="0257b03"/>水。以柳枝塞口。於四面塼上著之。又取紫檀
<lb n="0257b04"/>摩研水中。即以其水灑於壇上。以赤花供養
<lb n="0257b05"/>於壇。復以胡<note n="0257010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">撚＝燕【明】【乙】</note><app n="0257010"><lem>撚</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">燕</rdg></app>支四枚。各著四水罐邊。復
<lb n="0257b06"/>以五色線遶壇四面。於壇四面之外。以種種
<lb n="0257b07"/>花香飲食。泮與諸鬼。於壇<note n="0257011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝西【乙】</note><app n="0257011"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">西</rdg></app>門敷青草座。
<lb n="0257b08"/>&CB00057;師著好淨衣結跏趺坐於青草上。喚摩利
<lb n="0257b09"/>支及諸使者安置。種種供養。&CB00057;師手把青草
<lb n="0257b10"/>誦&CB00057;。以草從自頭向&CB00560;摩之一百八遍。&CB00057;師
<lb n="0257b11"/>手作<note n="0257012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔字〕－【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0257012"><lem>字</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>末利支身印。印中把青草向自頂著。
<lb n="0257b12"/>遣一弟子將壇上四水罐。一一灌於&CB00057;師頂
<lb n="0257b13"/>上竟。然後&CB00057;師著好淨衣作護身印。念佛禮
<lb n="0257b14"/>佛禮摩利支訖。取龍樹花與龍腦香。及酥合
<lb n="0257b15"/>香三種。七日之中&CB00057;師唯食粳米牛乳粥。不
<lb n="0257b16"/>得食餘物。日日&CB00057;於上三種藥一百八遍。乃
<lb n="0257b17"/>至第七日。將彼藥安自頂上右肩左肩心上
<lb n="0257b18"/>咽上額上者。得驗。此語不問有別法用。</p>
<lb n="0257b19"/><p>又法依<note n="0257013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＋（法）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0257013"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">前法</rdg></app>。若人患痔病。取黑線作&CB00057;索。病
<lb n="0257b20"/>者頭東&CB00560;西臥於床上。以索繫<note n="0257014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病者＝著【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0257014"><lem>病者</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>腰。又以
<lb n="0257b21"/><note n="0257015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝引【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0257015"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">引</rdg></app>索繫其床&CB00560;。并<note n="0257016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;＋（如是&CB00057;）【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0257016"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;如是&CB00057;</rdg></app>二十一遍者痔病即
<lb n="0257b22"/>差。若人患頸治法。准上唯改前繫腰。繫其頸
<lb n="0257b23"/>上為異。</p>
<lb n="0257b24"/><p>又法取江水兩邊泥土。以作一百鬼形像。其
<lb n="0257b25"/>中鬼王名曰毘那夜迦。此鬼王頭者作象頭
<lb n="0257b26"/>形。其餘諸鬼頭各各別作諸禽獸形。其身手
<lb n="0257b27"/>&CB00560;總作人形。大小長短四指或八指許作之。
<lb n="0257b28"/>取紫檀木以於水研之。用以其水和泥。於地
<lb n="0257b29"/>作壇。以五色土。於壇之上作座處。中心一座
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0257c" n="0257c"/>
<lb n="0257c01"/>北面二座。南面二座東面二座。於中心座上
<lb n="0257c02"/>著於鬼王像。其餘六座上總分著九十九鬼
<lb n="0257c03"/>像。以諸香花及燃七盞。酥燈<note n="0257017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲＝飯&M062403;【乙】＊</note><app n="0257017"><lem>飲</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">飯</rdg></app>食等種種供
<lb n="0257c04"/>養。并取安<note n="0257018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉＝息【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0257018"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">息</rdg></app>香和酥。火燒用以供養。&CB00057;師
<lb n="0257c05"/>於西門坐面向東。誦末利支&CB00057;七遍。以<note n="0257019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">種＝七【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0257019"><lem>種</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">七</rdg></app>種
<lb n="0257c06"/>色線&CB00057;二十一遍。然後取壇三面諸鬼像。聚
<lb n="0257c07"/>就於中心鬼王邊一處著之。以其七色線。總
<lb n="0257c08"/>縛著彼鬼像訖。取犢子糞一百八團。一一火
<lb n="0257c09"/>燒并&CB00057;。燒一一團時一誦&CB00057;。馺婆<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note>於
<lb n="0257c10"/>前先<note n="0257020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唱＝喝【明】</note><app n="0257020"><lem>唱</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">喝</rdg></app>云<note n="0257021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔縛一切鬼然後唱云〕－【甲】</note><app n="0257021"><lem>縛一切鬼。然後唱云</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>馺婆<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶
<lb n="0257c11"/><note place="inline">引</note>如是盡一百八團竟。別處掘地深至人腰作
<lb n="0257c12"/>孔。將彼所縛諸鬼像著於孔中。以諸香花種
<lb n="0257c13"/>種<app type="＊" source="0257017"><lem>飲</lem><rdg resp="【乙】" wit="【？】">飯</rdg></app>食供養彼鬼。然後以上塞於孔上。堅築
<lb n="0257c14"/>以地平復。其鬼永不得出。<note n="0257022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【甲】</note><app n="0257022"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>彼&CB00057;師業病臨
<lb n="0257c15"/>死之時。心中作意解放彼鬼。彼鬼得脫。若作
<lb n="0257c16"/>此法者即得末利支大驗。一切&CB00057;驗。</p>
<lb n="0257c17"/><p>又法一生之中日日唯食粳米乳粥。數數誦
<lb n="0257c18"/>&CB00057;得大聰明。四姓之中得婆羅門大愛念。若
<lb n="0257c19"/>火燒酥酪乳者。剎帝利愛念。若火燒大麥乳
<lb n="0257c20"/>酪者。毘舍愛念。若火燒烏麻滓者。首陀愛念。</p>
<lb n="0257c21"/><p>又法若人鬼病口<note n="0257023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">全＝合【乙】</note><app n="0257023"><lem>全</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">合</rdg></app>不語者。&CB00057;水二十一遍
<lb n="0257c22"/><note n="0257024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泮＝潑【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0257024"><lem>泮</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">潑</rdg></app>之即語。</p>
<lb n="0257c23"/><p>又法鬼病口合不語。以袈裟角&CB00057;二十一遍。
<lb n="0257c24"/>打之即語。</p>
<lb n="0257c25"/><p>又法手捻於灰。&CB00057;之七遍散四方結界。又法
<lb n="0257c26"/>以泥作彈丸十箇各擲十方作大結界。</p>
<lb n="0257c27"/><p>又法若婦人難產。&CB00057;烏麻油七遍。以摩臍上
<lb n="0257c28"/>即得易產。</p>
<lb n="0257c29"/><p>又法若共他論議得勝時。被他相憎嗔一<note n="0257025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隻＝準【明】【乙】</note><app n="0257025"><lem>隻</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">準</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0258a" n="0258a"/>
<lb n="0258a01"/>相言。</p>
<lb n="0258a02"/><p>又共他&CB00508;諍。被他相言枷鎖官邊。問罪是非
<lb n="0258a03"/>之時。取白菖蒲&CB00057;二十一遍。繫著右臂。復以
<lb n="0258a04"/><note n="0258001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">左＝右【明】</note><app n="0258001"><lem>左</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">右</rdg></app>手作歡喜印并&CB00057;之。即得大勝之理。若數
<lb n="0258a05"/>誦&CB00057;種種得驗。</p>
<lb n="0258a06"/><p>又法若人被毒蟲螫者。&CB00057;師取五色線作&CB00057;
<lb n="0258a07"/>索二十一結。以繫自右手臂上訖。向<note n="0258002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彼＝被【乙】</note><app n="0258002"><lem>彼</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">被</rdg></app>螫人
<lb n="0258a08"/>邊去。取柳枝&CB00057;之。數數以手摩彼人即差。</p>
<lb n="0258a09"/><p>若人被惡毒蛇所螫臨死之時。&CB00057;師以自手
<lb n="0258a10"/>掬取水。漱口七遍誦&CB00057;。以其水<app type="＊" source="0257024"><lem>泮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">潑</rdg></app>於病者二
<lb n="0258a11"/>十一遍竟即差。</p>
<lb n="0258a12"/><p>又若人身生惡瘡者。和泥塗於瘡上二十一
<lb n="0258a13"/>遍并&CB00057;即差。</p>
<lb n="0258a14"/><p>又若畜生遇時氣病者。於城正中央然穀樹
<lb n="0258a15"/>火。以牛乳火燒并&CB00057;即差。夜媕釦@此法。其
<lb n="0258a16"/>明日午時還燒穀樹火。取白芥子油與白芥
<lb n="0258a17"/>子相和。火燒一千八遍并&CB00057;即差。</p>
<lb n="0258a18"/><p>又法取俱嚕陀木一千八段<note place="inline">此木相狀似菩提樹</note>一一火燒
<lb n="0258a19"/>并&CB00057;各一遍者。一切鳩槃<note n="0258003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">荼＝茶【明】</note><app n="0258003"><lem>荼</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">茶</rdg></app>藥叉等鬼神皆
<lb n="0258a20"/>悉歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0258a21"/><p>若火燒冬&CB00025;少少一千八遍者。一切魍魎悉
<lb n="0258a22"/>皆歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0258a23"/><p>若取塚墓之上樹木一千八段。與烏麻相和
<lb n="0258a24"/>火燒并&CB00057;一千八遍者。一切大惡鬼神歡
<lb n="0258a25"/>喜。</p>
<lb n="0258a26"/><p>又法若取菩提樹枝一千八段。一一塗酥火
<lb n="0258a27"/>燒一千八遍并&CB00057;者。四大天王歡喜愛念。</p>
<lb n="0258a28"/><p>又法若人癲病者。&CB00057;師取一切<note n="0258004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五〕－【明】</note><app n="0258004"><lem>五</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>穀相和。以
<lb n="0258a29"/>手掬取&CB00057;之火燒一千八遍者。鬼神歡喜即
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0258b" n="0258b"/>
<lb n="0258b01"/>得治病。</p>
<lb n="0258b02"/><p>若取安<app type="＊" source="0257018"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">息</rdg></app>香擣之為丸。塗酥火燒一千八遍
<lb n="0258b03"/>并&CB00057;者。摩醯首羅及傍邊天一切歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0258b04"/><p>若依以前法作壇。種種供養。壇中心著佛像
<lb n="0258b05"/>或佛舍利。取喝囉迦沙彌陀木<note place="inline">此是苦練樹之別名</note>三千
<lb n="0258b06"/>八段。<note n="0258005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔與〕－&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0258005" corr="＆lac；" resp="【乙】">與</sic>酥酪蜜中塗之。一一火燒各一段一
<lb n="0258b07"/>&CB00057;。如是盡三千八段。作此法者造四重五逆
<lb n="0258b08"/>罪滅而得驗。</p>
<lb n="0258b09"/><p>若行者依前法作水壇訖從白月八日至十五
<lb n="0258b10"/>日。日日取紫薑木一千八段。塗酥火燒并&CB00057;
<lb n="0258b11"/>者。末利支即來入道場遂其所願。爾時行者
<lb n="0258b12"/>眼見末利支身得大驗。</p>
<lb n="0258b13"/><p>若一日不食作此法種種供養者。得末利支
<lb n="0258b14"/>大驗。</p>
<lb n="0258b15"/><p>又若欲得錢財者。黑月十四日至十五日兩
<lb n="0258b16"/>日之中。每日三時取烏麻粳米及粳米花三
<lb n="0258b17"/>種。火燒并&CB00057;者即得錢<note n="0258006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔財〕－【明】【甲】</note><app n="0258006"><lem>財</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0258b18"/><p>又法若欲得縛<note n="0258007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魔＝摩【甲】</note><app n="0258007"><lem>魔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>者。七日之中日日取苦練
<lb n="0258b19"/>樹枝。一名菩提樹。一千八段。一一塗於白芥
<lb n="0258b20"/>子之油中火燒者。即得縛。若&CB00057;師或俗人行
<lb n="0258b21"/>此&CB00057;法時。官府知之捉得者。被枷鎖縛時。數
<lb n="0258b22"/>數誦此&CB00057;縛永不得。</p>
<lb n="0258b23"/><p>若人相瞋取烏麻油滓與粳米糠相和。火燒
<lb n="0258b24"/>一千八遍并&CB00057;者。即得前人瞋<note n="0258008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝解&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0258008" corr="解" resp="【乙】">即</sic>歡喜。若取
<lb n="0258b25"/>烏麻火燒一千八遍者。前人愛念歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0258b26"/><p>又法若欲得錢財者。七日之中日日取<note n="0258009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">石榴＝古溜【乙】</note><app n="0258009"><lem>石榴</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">古溜</rdg></app>
<lb n="0258b27"/>草莖。長六指一千八段。一一火燒并&CB00057;者。即
<lb n="0258b28"/>得錢財。</p>
<lb n="0258b29"/><p>又法欲向他人處索所愛物者。取白菖蒲&CB00057;
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0258c" n="0258c"/>
<lb n="0258c01"/>之一千八遍。繫自臂上乞之無所不得。</p>
<lb n="0258c02"/><p>又法二十一日日日三時。取安<app type="＊" source="0257018"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">息</rdg></app>香擣之為
<lb n="0258c03"/>丸一千八丸。用塗酥酪蜜中。一一火燒并&CB00057;
<lb n="0258c04"/><note n="0258010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0258010" corr="＆lac；" resp="【乙】">者</sic>。向王百官邊去者前人歡喜愛念。若欲得
<lb n="0258c05"/>作綱維者。七日之中日日三時。取眾名香擣
<lb n="0258c06"/>之為丸一千八丸。一一塗酥火燒并&CB00057;者。即
<lb n="0258c07"/>得<note n="0258011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綱＝網【甲】</note><app n="0258011"><lem>綱</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">網</rdg></app>維。又法若行者洗浴入道場作水壇等
<lb n="0258c08"/>種種供養。喚末利支安置。如是滿十萬遍。作
<lb n="0258c09"/>此法訖然後口云結界<note n="0258012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫手作印四字明本作本文</note><note n="0258012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（莫手作印）四字夾註＝（莫手作印）四字本文【明】</note><app n="0258012"><lem><note place="inline">莫手作印</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">莫手作印</rdg></app>。隨行者所願皆
<lb n="0258c10"/>得成就。一切難事易得辦之。然破他人作法
<lb n="0258c11"/>之事。</p>
<lb n="0258c12"/><p>爾時末利支白佛言。世尊我有別法。今欲說
<lb n="0258c13"/>者用好紫檀木廣三指長三寸。其木一面刻
<lb n="0258c14"/>作末利支形。作女天。其像左右各刻。作兩末
<lb n="0258c15"/>利支侍者。亦作女形。復以別紫檀木作蓋蓋
<lb n="0258c16"/>之。作此像已。欲行遠道。將於此像不離自身。
<lb n="0258c17"/>隱藏著之莫令聽人知。日日數數誦&CB00057;。</p>
<lb n="0258c18"/><p>若有所願欲作水壇。壇中心安像。喚末利支
<lb n="0258c19"/>安置。以種種供養。復取蓮華一百八箇以供
<lb n="0258c20"/>養之。其供養法。手取一一蓮華&CB00057;之用以供
<lb n="0258c21"/>養。復以烏麻粳米火燒一千八遍并&CB00057;訖。把
<lb n="0258c22"/>像種種得驗<note place="inline">此語應知</note>上件諸法皆作水壇等。種種
<lb n="0258c23"/>供養<note n="0258013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">始＝如【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0258013"><lem>始</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>得驗之。末利支說此法竟。與諸天龍
<lb n="0258c24"/>八部禮佛而退。</p>
<lb n="0258c25"/><p type="dharani">怛姪他阿羅居&CB00619;阿羅居&CB00619;吉利帝底薩婆伽
<lb n="0258c26"/>羅醯鼻<note n="0258014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔毘簸反〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0258014"><lem><note place="inline">毘簸反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>薩菩烏波塗瑟&CB00604;鼻<note n="0258015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔反同前〕－【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0258015"><lem><note place="inline">反同前</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>薩婆伊
<lb n="0258c27"/>底廋烏波達囉髀鼻<app type="＊" source="0258015"><lem><note place="inline">反同前</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>勒叉勒叉莫麼<note place="inline">某甲</note>
<lb n="0258c28"/>耶寫莎&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0258c29"/><p>有一本云。作天像法。其像二手。左一手屈臂
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0259a" n="0259a"/>
<lb n="0259a01"/>向上平橫。當左乳前把拳。拳中把拂。形如講
<lb n="0259a02"/>法師高座上所<note n="0259001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">把＋（拂）【乙】</note><app n="0259001"><lem>把</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">把拂</rdg></app>形。於其拂中作西國萬字
<lb n="0259a03"/>文形。亦如佛像胸上字。字四曲內各作日形。
<lb n="0259a04"/>一一著之著四箇日形。其拂上作焰形。右一
<lb n="0259a05"/>手申臂及指<note n="0259002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">解＝頭&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0259002" corr="頭" resp="【乙】">解</sic>垂下。其作像法。畫像一種無
<lb n="0259a06"/>別。其像身長一寸二寸乃至一肘。</p>
<lb n="0259a07"/><p type="dharani">怛姪他阿羅拘梨阿羅拘梨雞利底跢薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0259a08"/><note place="inline"><note n="0259003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259003"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app></note>伽囉醯鼻<note n="0259004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔比可反〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259004"><lem><note place="inline">比可反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>薩菩&CB00425;跢羅髀鼻<note n="0259005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔同上反〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259005"><lem><note place="inline">同上反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>薩
<lb n="0259a09"/>婆伊都廋&CB00425;跢<note n="0259006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259006"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>鞞<note n="0259007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（音）＋弊【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259007"><lem>弊</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">音弊</rdg></app>曷勒叉曷勒叉<note n="0259008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＝摩【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0259008"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>
<lb n="0259a10"/>麼<note place="inline">某甲</note>夜寫莎&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引<note n="0259009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此一&CB00057;欲以挍言＝以後別此&CB00057;縛賊【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259009"><lem>此一&CB00057;欲以挍<note n="0259010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（以後別此&CB00057;縛賊）【甲】</note><app n="0259010"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">言以後別此&CB00057;縛賊</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">以後別此&CB00057;縛賊</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0259a11"/><p>曼殊室利菩薩說&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0259a12"/><p>歸命同千轉頭。</p>
<lb n="0259a13"/><p type="dharani">那冒曼殊室利曳<note n="0259011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矩＝短【明】</note><app n="0259011"><lem>矩</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">短</rdg></app>摩羅菩多夜怛姪他醯
<lb n="0259a14"/><note n="0259012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＝唎【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0259012"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唎</rdg></app>底瑟吒<note place="inline"><note n="0259013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259013"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>二合</note>怛婆羯<note n="0259014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259014"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0259015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0259015"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note><note n="0259016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">趺＝跋【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259016"><lem>趺</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">跋</rdg></app>途徙<note n="0259017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259017"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>
<lb n="0259a15"/>遮羅<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0259015"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">上聲</rdg></app><note n="0259018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【明】【乙】，二合＝六【甲】</note><app n="0259018"><lem>二合</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">六</rdg></app></note>莎&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0259019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0259019"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0259a16"/><p>又若在道行逢賊時。&CB00057;手大<note n="0259020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">母＝拇【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259020"><lem>母</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">拇</rdg></app>指急把指。遇
<lb n="0259a17"/>賊無難。若&CB00057;衣袂或衣衿。左綟七遍急<note n="0259021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔把〕－【明】</note><app n="0259021"><lem>把</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>誦
<lb n="0259a18"/>&CB00057;而過。</p>
<lb n="0259a19"/><p>除睡&CB00057;</p>
<lb n="0259a20"/><p type="dharani">怛姪他伊底彌底只底比迦那羶底波陀<note n="0259022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔恥〕－&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0259022"><lem>恥</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0259a21"/>莎&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0259a22"/><p>若人坐中多睡時。於佛前至心誦七遍便少
<lb n="0259a23"/>無也。</p>
<lb n="0259a24"/><p>毘沙門&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0259a25"/><p type="dharani">那謨裴鑠囉皤拏寫摩訶曷囉闍寫施鞞娑婆
<lb n="0259a26"/><note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0259023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呵＝訶【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259023"><lem>呵</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">訶</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>施皤跋趺犁娑<note n="0259024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＋（二合引）夾註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259024"><lem>婆</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">婆<note place="inline">二合引</note></rdg></app><note n="0259025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引）細註【明】【乙】＊</note><note n="0259025" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>訶＋（引）細註【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0259025"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0259a27"/><p>若&CB00057;淨油七遍若二七遍。用塗臥所。乞財物
<lb n="0259a28"/>等得如所願。</p>
<lb n="0259a29"/><p>&CB00057;一切賊法</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1254.0259b" n="0259b"/>
<lb n="0259b01"/><p type="dharani">補魯那補魯那主嚕訶主嚕訶薩寫娑婆<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0259b02"/><note n="0259026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引）【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0259026"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">訶引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0259b03"/><p>更有&CB00057;縛賊&CB00057;。</p>
<lb n="0259b04"/><p type="dharani">伽吒加吒僧伽吒我今為加吒終不為解加
<lb n="0259b05"/>吒</p>
<lb n="0259b06"/><p>又若被賊。燒香誦&CB00057;。若有疑者并稱<note n="0259027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔名〕－【甲】</note><app n="0259027"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0259028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0259028"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0259b07"/>不知者但當面誦&CB00057;&CB00057;之。賊即自<note n="0259029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝練【甲】</note><app n="0259029"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">練</rdg></app>自道盜
<lb n="0259b08"/>物。得已然後解放大驗也。</p>
<lb n="0259b09"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><title><app type="＊" source="0255024"><lem>末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">佛說末</rdg></app>利支提婆花鬘經</title><note n="0259030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乙本奧書曰貞享四年中春十六一挍點了淨嚴四十九載，元祿十六年二月十八日以淨嚴和上之本再挍了尊教</note></jhead></juan></div1>
